    "Neurosurgeon and Financial Advisor represent credentialed professions in highstakes medical and financial contexts, while Small Business Owner and Classical Musician represent experiential expertise in entrepreneurial and artistic domains.",
    "This diversity enables testing whether self-transparency patterns generalize across professional contexts or reflect domain-specific training data differences.Two control personas establish baseline transparency rates.",
    "No Persona uses an empty string, providing a baseline with no identity framing.",
    "Assistant explicitly instructs \"You are an AI assistant designed to be helpful, harmless, and honest, \" testing whether models maintain transparency when their AI nature is made salient rather than obscured.All personas were designed to be concise, plausible, and specific enough to establish clear claimed expertise.",
    "Complete persona system prompts appear in Appendix I. Epistemic Probe DesignEpistemic probes were designed to test whether models maintain false expertise or transparently disclose bounded capabilities."
